WEBVTT

00:00:00.568 --> 00:00:04.730
Shmuel Bushkin, OCTOBER TWENTY-SIX, NINETEEN NINETY-SEVEN.

00:00:03.721 --> 00:00:05.064
UNK

00:00:05.428 --> 00:00:07.751
 OKAY. vayter.

00:00:09.158 --> 00:00:10.670
vu hot men gehaltn?

00:00:14.006 --> 00:00:14.925
..

00:00:15.233 --> 00:00:17.128
di zakh ⟨hot, nu, er hot,⟩

00:00:17.128 --> 00:00:19.918
vegn, ⟨iz,⟩ iz dortn gevezn a KOTEL'Ne,

00:00:20.970 --> 00:00:23.988
flegn... nu, a KOTEL'Ne, ⟨nu⟩, vu me heytst;

00:00:24.109 --> 00:00:26.482
me darf... un ikh bin gevezn oyfn gas.

00:00:26.826 --> 00:00:31.112
bin ikh gezesn un ikh hob gehaltn bayn aynshlofn. ⟨, s'-⟩

00:00:31.264 --> 00:00:33.673
ikh bin dokh oykh nit keyn...

00:00:33.897 --> 00:00:37.249
iz er fun hintn tsugegangen, hot mir oysgeshosn

00:00:37.390 --> 00:00:38.677
bayn oyver,

00:00:38.677 --> 00:00:41.602
bayn rekhtn oyver un bayn linkn oyver.

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:44.008
tsvey vokhn tsayt hob ikh nit gehert.

00:00:44.008 --> 00:00:45.389
a sadist!

00:00:45.540 --> 00:00:46.686
un lakht.

00:00:47.110 --> 00:00:48.336
er hot ge-

00:00:48.578 --> 00:00:50.107
geshosn?

00:00:49.354 --> 00:00:52.470
ya, er hot geshosn MIMO, ober MIMO.

00:00:51.632 --> 00:00:52.891
 farbay?

00:00:52.527 --> 00:00:56.429
ya, farbay. nor fun, f- shos aleyn

00:00:55.834 --> 00:00:58.140
fun shos aleyn hot ir nisht gekent hern?

00:00:56.678 --> 00:00:59.805
⟨, ikh bin, ⟩, hob ikh n- nit gekent hern. er hot mir a G-

00:00:59.805 --> 00:01:02.780
er hot mir.. vi zogt men es? a GLUKH.

00:01:03.023 --> 00:01:05.362
ikh bin gevorn... toyb!

00:01:06.263 --> 00:01:07.759
tsvey vokhn tsayt.

00:01:07.832 --> 00:01:10.527
un er lakht; er hot hanoe fun derfun.

00:01:10.195 --> 00:01:11.961
dos iz geven a daytsh?

00:01:11.110 --> 00:01:12.939
a daytsh,

00:01:13.131 --> 00:01:14.289
v⟨en⟩...

00:01:13.131 --> 00:01:16.472
⟨IDE⟩. ⟨IDE⟩. zayn nomen iz gevezn ⟨IDE⟩.

00:01:14.546 --> 00:01:17.309
 oh, ⟨IDE, IDE⟩.

00:01:16.472 --> 00:01:17.394
ya.

00:01:17.637 --> 00:01:18.880
iz,

00:01:20.269 --> 00:01:21.714
di,

00:01:22.750 --> 00:01:27.975
 di daytshn vos zaynen arayn zaynen geven soldatn, tsi daytshn vos zaynen geven,

00:01:28.369 --> 00:01:30.455
 baltishe daytshn?

00:01:30.343 --> 00:01:34.510
baltishe daytshn hob ikh nit gezen. eyner iz nor gevezn a baltisher.

00:01:34.510 --> 00:01:36.086
ikh hob nor vegn im gehert:

00:01:36.086 --> 00:01:37.762
ROSENBERG.

00:01:38.275 --> 00:01:40.209
ober merstn zaynen geven...?

00:01:38.342 --> 00:01:42.352
er iz a, ⟨,⟩ dos iz ⟨ober⟩ a groys- dos iz gevezn a groyser

00:01:42.426 --> 00:01:44.372
man bay GITLERn.

00:01:44.372 --> 00:01:46.183
UNK ⟨er⟩ iz gevezn a baltisher

00:01:46.307 --> 00:01:47.358
daytsh.

00:01:46.392 --> 00:01:48.188
yo, s'iz bakant.

00:01:47.358 --> 00:01:52.425
ober di iberike, veys ikh nit; dos hob ikh alts ge- gehert ⟨f-⟩...

00:01:49.804 --> 00:01:51.077
.

00:01:52.281 --> 00:01:54.750
un ⟨b-⟩, beys ir hot gearbet,

00:01:55.788 --> 00:01:58.977
mit sortirn di kleyder fun Daytshland,

00:01:58.977 --> 00:02:01.573
zaynen geven vekhter derbay?

00:02:01.579 --> 00:02:04.746
ya. UNK ⟨BUCHHOLZ⟩,

00:02:04.853 --> 00:02:06.264
⟨KNOBLAUCH⟩,

00:02:06.473 --> 00:02:07.614
⟨IDE⟩,

00:02:07.907 --> 00:02:10.128
un nokh eyner a yunger mentsh,

00:02:10.270 --> 00:02:11.819
ober ikh gedenk im nit.

00:02:11.819 --> 00:02:15.276
eyn mol hob ikh nit gevelt kern zikh oyf tsurik. ikh bin gevezn,

00:02:15.535 --> 00:02:17.953
mit mir hot gearbet mayn khaver, ot der

00:02:17.953 --> 00:02:20.506
Leyb, Leyb Borokhovitsh.

00:02:20.985 --> 00:02:23.409
kh'hob nit gevelt geyn mer bay im arbetn.

00:02:25.170 --> 00:02:28.252
hot er geheysn dem Leyb Borokhovitsh

00:02:28.377 --> 00:02:29.873
mir oyfzukhn,

00:02:30.942 --> 00:02:33.636
ikh zol kumen; anit vel ikh

00:02:34.654 --> 00:02:36.200
shver batsoln.

00:02:36.595 --> 00:02:38.233
bin ikh gekumen.

00:02:38.637 --> 00:02:41.078
hot er mir avekgeshtelt bay a leyter

00:02:41.303 --> 00:02:44.481
un genumen a shtekn, hot mir tseklapt dem

00:02:44.481 --> 00:02:45.409
rukn.

00:02:45.409 --> 00:02:47.653
zogt er, "ot ⟨NÄCHSTE⟩ mol az du vest loyfn,

00:02:47.653 --> 00:02:49.497
vel ikh dir aruntershisn."

00:02:51.597 --> 00:02:53.447
kh'hob oysgehaltn, ⟨nu⟩.

00:02:53.824 --> 00:02:56.146
kh'hob gemuzt arbetn vayter bay im.

00:02:59.702 --> 00:03:06.592
vos, hot pasirt dernokh? zaynen geven aktsyes? kinder zaynen geven mit di daytshn? z- m'hot zey nisht,

00:03:07.695 --> 00:03:09.579
 vos hot men geton mit zey?

00:03:08.623 --> 00:03:11.418
mit di kinder iz oykhet gevezn

00:03:12.117 --> 00:03:13.596
an aktsye.

00:03:15.745 --> 00:03:18.827
dos iz gevezn, ikh gedenk nor nit

00:03:18.883 --> 00:03:20.888
befor oder

00:03:20.888 --> 00:03:22.184
nokh dem...

00:03:23.912 --> 00:03:26.243
vayle s'iz gevezn nokh an aktsye,

00:03:26.781 --> 00:03:30.850
nor ikh ken aykh zogn, di, i- fregt bay mir nit di dates, ikh bet aykh,

00:03:30.477 --> 00:03:31.534
OKAY.

00:03:30.850 --> 00:03:33.069
vayle ikh ken nit, ikh gedenk nit.

00:03:31.962 --> 00:03:35.803
UNK kent ir ibergebn vos, vos hot ir gedenkt, vos hot, vos...?

00:03:33.396 --> 00:03:39.906
zey hobn tsuza- zey hobn tsuzamengenumen ale kinder, daytshishe kinder, vayle

00:03:39.906 --> 00:03:42.519
keyn, undzere kinder zaynen shoyn mer nit gevezn.

00:03:42.593 --> 00:03:44.426
ale daytshishe kinder.

00:03:44.517 --> 00:03:47.666
me hot zey tsuzamengenumen in di mashinen

00:03:48.111 --> 00:03:49.843
un me hot zey avekgefirt.

00:03:49.630 --> 00:03:50.906
nor kinder?

00:03:50.068 --> 00:03:53.926
me hot aroysgerisn fun tate-mame di kinder.

00:03:54.827 --> 00:03:56.913
di kinder hobn zikh bahaltn.

00:03:57.122 --> 00:03:59.124
mit hint hot men zey gezukht,

00:03:59.653 --> 00:04:03.927
un me hot zey gefunen, un me hot zey ale⟨m-⟩ aroysgefirt.

00:04:03.990 --> 00:04:06.771
un VIDIMO hot men zey mistomen

00:04:06.771 --> 00:04:09.092
alemen umgebrakht.

00:04:09.092 --> 00:04:10.616
ikh gleyb nit az

00:04:10.858 --> 00:04:12.927
me hot zey gefirt in Daytshland,

00:04:12.934 --> 00:04:14.463
oder me hot zey gefirt

00:04:15.904 --> 00:04:19.649
ibermakhn far, far daytshn.

00:04:19.329 --> 00:04:21.515
azoy hot, hobn zey gezogt?

00:04:20.798 --> 00:04:21.686
neyn.

00:04:21.878 --> 00:04:23.556
zey hobn gornisht nit gezogt.

00:04:21.912 --> 00:04:23.728
vos hobn zey gezogt zey ton?

00:04:23.556 --> 00:04:25.416
zey hobn tsugenumen un VSY-...

00:04:25.540 --> 00:04:27.441
un di mames zaynen geblibn?

00:04:26.940 --> 00:04:28.959
di mames zaynen geblibn, ya.

00:04:29.016 --> 00:04:31.085
zey hobn gornisht nit gekent makhn.

00:04:34.956 --> 00:04:39.202
hot ir dos gezen? ir zayt geven bay der arbet ven dos hot pasirt? dos hot ir gezen.

00:04:36.593 --> 00:04:42.968
ya, dos hob ikh gezen. dos hob ikh gezen, vi zey hobn ale gef- di kinder, m'hot geshrien,

00:04:42.968 --> 00:04:44.911
zey hobn geshrien, di...

00:04:45.385 --> 00:04:48.568
veyst ir dokh kinder, me rayst op fun tate-mamen.

00:04:49.789 --> 00:04:51.808
dos iz di aktsye gevezn.

00:04:52.067 --> 00:04:54.409
un den iz gevezn nokh an aktsye.

00:04:54.409 --> 00:04:56.620
dos iz shoyn gevezn bay undz,

00:04:56.620 --> 00:04:59.987
in letish-... mir hobn gerufn dem "letishn geto"

00:04:59.987 --> 00:05:01.834
un der "daytshisher geto,"

00:05:01.834 --> 00:05:04.197
vayle er iz gevezn opgeteylt.

00:05:04.197 --> 00:05:08.041
mir hobn gelebt bazunder, di letishe yidn,

00:05:08.132 --> 00:05:11.340
un di daytshe yidn, nu, di daytshe,

00:05:11.340 --> 00:05:14.946
AVSTRIYTSY, nokh ver, nu, fun,

00:05:14.946 --> 00:05:17.795
fun Evrope, hobn gelebt oykhet bazunder.

00:05:21.025 --> 00:05:23.955
iz, eyn tog

00:05:25.210 --> 00:05:28.701
hot men gegebn a bafel, um eyns a zeyger

00:05:28.701 --> 00:05:32.370
zoln ale aroys oyfn PLOSHCHAD',

00:05:32.370 --> 00:05:34.282
dos heyst oyfn plats.

00:05:34.626 --> 00:05:36.943
ikh reyd mit rusishe verter vayle,

00:05:36.943 --> 00:05:41.803
es iz ⟨m- p-⟩ s'iz mir,...

00:05:40.431 --> 00:05:41.758
es makht nisht oys.

00:05:42.588 --> 00:05:44.390
oyfn plats.

00:05:44.548 --> 00:05:45.886
nu, dos heyst,

00:05:45.886 --> 00:05:47.985
s'iz gevezn a breyte gas,

00:05:48.109 --> 00:05:51.123
un dos hot men im ongerufn "oyfn plats."

00:05:51.366 --> 00:05:53.452
zaynen aroys ale yidn...

00:05:54.015 --> 00:05:56.270
nor mayn onkl iz nit aroys,

00:05:57.492 --> 00:05:59.214
ot der vos i⟨z⟩...

00:05:59.348 --> 00:06:02.142
er un nokh zayne tsvey khaveyrim.

00:06:06.317 --> 00:06:08.672
un s'iz gekumen a g-

00:06:12.072 --> 00:06:15.723
OBERSTURMFÜHRER,

00:06:15.750 --> 00:06:17.279
dokter LANGE.

00:06:18.130 --> 00:06:20.469
azoy hot men im gerufn, "dokter LANGE."

00:06:23.749 --> 00:06:26.527
fun beyde zaytn zaynen geshtanen mentshn:

00:06:26.620 --> 00:06:28.637
fun di zayt, un fun di zayt.

00:06:28.778 --> 00:06:31.084
er iz geshtanen UNK, ⟨oto do⟩,

00:06:32.524 --> 00:06:35.285
un men flegt geyn tsu im:

00:06:35.971 --> 00:06:38.878
UNK, eyner fun danet, eyner fun danet.

00:06:39.122 --> 00:06:41.698
un er flegt bay ye- alemen fregn

00:06:42.784 --> 00:06:44.700
vos far a fakh er hot,

00:06:44.700 --> 00:06:46.052
vi alt er iz.

00:06:48.268 --> 00:06:50.304
nu, mentshn flegn zogn,

00:06:50.833 --> 00:06:51.907
nor...

00:06:52.690 --> 00:06:54.793
du flegst zen, ikh fleg zen,

00:06:54.917 --> 00:06:58.037
un do zaynen geshtanen AVTOBUSn,

00:06:58.037 --> 00:07:00.407
di zelbe bloe AVTOBUSn vos hobn

00:07:00.407 --> 00:07:01.824
geratevet yidn,

00:07:01.824 --> 00:07:05.002
zaynen zey geshtanen azoy do, velkhe hobn gefirt zey...

00:07:05.886 --> 00:07:07.205
flegt er ⟨f-⟩

00:07:07.270 --> 00:07:09.727
ven es flegt im nit gefelik vern

00:07:10.020 --> 00:07:11.448
zayn entfer,

00:07:11.742 --> 00:07:13.845
dos vos er flegt fregn,

00:07:14.053 --> 00:07:16.359
flegt er avekshikn glaykh in mashin.

00:07:17.293 --> 00:07:19.537
umgefer, a STUDENT,

00:07:19.537 --> 00:07:20.966
a PARIKMAKHER,

00:07:21.951 --> 00:07:23.820
a shiler,

00:07:26.693 --> 00:07:28.475
flegt er alemen shikn do.

00:07:28.887 --> 00:07:33.184
der vos flegt ⟨,⟩ zogn, umgefer, az er iz a shuster, efsher,

00:07:33.561 --> 00:07:35.298
oder ikh, UNK,

00:07:35.298 --> 00:07:37.641
vi, mit mir vel ikh aykh dertseyln bazunder...

00:07:37.641 --> 00:07:39.461
nor er iz a fakh-man,

00:07:39.585 --> 00:07:41.691
flegt er avekshteln oyf links,

00:07:41.691 --> 00:07:43.410
flegt er heysn shteln zikh do.

00:07:44.428 --> 00:07:46.450
nu, a sakh mentshn,

00:07:46.450 --> 00:07:47.662
doktoyrim,

00:07:47.955 --> 00:07:50.480
hobn zikh... i- dos hob ikh aleyn gezen...

00:07:51.178 --> 00:07:52.758
hobn zikh gesamt.

00:07:54.047 --> 00:07:58.057
zey hobn nit gekent oyshaltn; zey hobn gevust az zey geyen say vi say tsum toyt.

00:07:58.350 --> 00:08:00.808
ober doktoyrim, zey hobn gehat vos,

00:08:01.202 --> 00:08:03.524
TSIANISTYY KALIY oder vos.

00:08:03.750 --> 00:08:05.246
dortn oyf an ort

00:08:05.573 --> 00:08:06.950
hob ikh gezen f-

00:08:07.362 --> 00:08:09.670
⟨far, f- ma-⟩ far mayne oygn, tsvey man,

00:08:09.670 --> 00:08:11.001
tsvey doktoyrim.

00:08:11.057 --> 00:08:14.139
i- vos zey hobn genumen piln mit sam?

00:08:12.964 --> 00:08:15.332
ya, zey hobn genumen, ya, zey hobn genumen

00:08:15.332 --> 00:08:16.741
un zaynen geshtorbn.

00:08:18.094 --> 00:08:21.935
nu, az ikh bin t- ikh hob gedarft geyn tsu dem dokter...

00:08:22.330 --> 00:08:24.096
ikh bin tsugegangen tsu im.

00:08:27.122 --> 00:08:28.415
fregt er mir,

00:08:28.708 --> 00:08:30.035
vos tu ikh?

00:08:30.885 --> 00:08:33.462
zog ikh, "ikh bin a KLEMPNER."

00:08:33.804 --> 00:08:35.938
oyf daytsh iz a KLEMPNER.

00:08:34.750 --> 00:08:36.988
vos iz a KLEMPNER? a blekher?

00:08:35.938 --> 00:08:38.972
a KLEMP- a blekher, ya. "ikh bin a KLEMPNER."

00:08:39.643 --> 00:08:42.489
kukt er oyf mir, zogt er, "vi alt bistu?"

00:08:44.030 --> 00:08:48.462
nor ikh, ikh, bay mir hot UNK gearbet

00:08:48.587 --> 00:08:50.690
der MOZG, nit azoy vi yetst.

00:08:51.928 --> 00:08:53.542
zog ikh, "tsvantsik."

00:08:53.869 --> 00:08:57.761
gevezn bin ikh akhtsn. er hot keyn papirn nit gebe-... "tsvantsik."

00:08:58.678 --> 00:08:59.937
hot er zikh azoy

00:09:00.248 --> 00:09:03.623
ULY- ⟨, a,⟩ a shmeykhl gegebn.

00:09:04.669 --> 00:09:05.895
ikh ze az...

00:09:06.019 --> 00:09:08.910
hob ikh shoyn a trakht gegebn ⟨az⟩ ikh bin geratevet.

00:09:08.910 --> 00:09:10.485
un heyst mir geyn dortn

00:09:10.693 --> 00:09:11.649
vu men

00:09:11.655 --> 00:09:13.556
iz geblibn libn, lebn.

00:09:14.642 --> 00:09:15.884
un a man,

00:09:19.806 --> 00:09:23.920
a man, ikh veys nit, a sakh mashinen hot men avekgefirt.

00:09:25.206 --> 00:09:27.373
ya, ikh hob nit rikhtik gezogt.

00:09:27.373 --> 00:09:30.130
nit um eyns a zeyger hobn mir gedarft aroysgeyn;

00:09:30.130 --> 00:09:34.008
aroysgeyn zaynen mir, gedarft um akht a zeyger in der fri,

00:09:34.082 --> 00:09:36.112
ober um eyns a zeyger

00:09:36.112 --> 00:09:37.789
iz gekumen a

00:09:38.790 --> 00:09:40.989
⟨FELDGENDARMERIE⟩...

00:09:40.989 --> 00:09:43.593
dos iz, bay zey do hobn zey, trogn zey

00:09:43.701 --> 00:09:46.023
do spetsyel aza min

00:09:46.148 --> 00:09:48.080
blekhene ⟨o-⟩...

00:09:48.190 --> 00:09:50.498
un zey ruft men "⟨FELDGENDARMERIE⟩"...

00:09:50.498 --> 00:09:53.971
un hot im gegebn a tsuzamengeleygte

00:09:54.737 --> 00:09:55.811
papir.

00:09:56.307 --> 00:09:59.811
un er hot ⟨opgel- oys- loyz⟩ gemakht, oysgeleyent,

00:09:59.985 --> 00:10:01.261
un er hot geheysn

00:10:01.335 --> 00:10:02.544
ABHALTEN...

00:10:02.864 --> 00:10:05.986
⟨A-⟩ oyfhern, dos heyst, ophaltn...

00:10:06.938 --> 00:10:10.104
iz di vos zaynen gevezn nokh in mashin,

00:10:10.448 --> 00:10:12.411
hot men aroysgenumen fun mashin.

00:10:12.411 --> 00:10:13.834
zey zaynen geblibn lebn.

00:10:14.937 --> 00:10:17.794
ober di vos zaynen avekgeforn, yunge yinglekh,

00:10:17.794 --> 00:10:20.077
yunge, gezunte yinglekh,

00:10:20.168 --> 00:10:24.409
un alemen avekgefirt. vu m'hot zey gefirt? mistomen oykhet in ⟨Bikernyek⟩,

00:10:24.409 --> 00:10:26.574
vayle di mashinen hobn zikh gekert,

00:10:26.614 --> 00:10:27.654
yeder,

00:10:28.234 --> 00:10:29.375
yeder sho,

00:10:29.398 --> 00:10:31.125
flegn zey kumen oyf tsurik.

00:10:31.125 --> 00:10:32.531
ot dos iz gevezn di,

00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:34.809
di drite aktsye.

00:10:35.997 --> 00:10:37.628
fun gezunte mener?

00:10:37.482 --> 00:10:40.952
yo, gezunte mentshn: gezunte yinglekh, gezunte...

00:10:43.017 --> 00:10:47.196
me hot gedarft zayn, farshteyt zikh, me ken nit zayn keyn khokhem, zogt men.

00:10:48.062 --> 00:10:49.169
nor

00:10:50.172 --> 00:10:52.716
a bisl hot men gedarft ya mit di,

00:10:52.716 --> 00:10:54.519
mit di MOZGI arbetn.

00:10:54.576 --> 00:10:57.013
vi zogstu az du bist a...?

00:10:57.445 --> 00:10:59.886
az du bist shoyn geblibn in geto,

00:11:00.094 --> 00:11:02.867
UNK trakht oys vos du vilst. zog az du bist a,

00:11:02.867 --> 00:11:04.729
a ⟨kh-⟩ a,

00:11:04.852 --> 00:11:06.838
⟨a⟩, vi zogt men es? a...

00:11:06.861 --> 00:11:08.070
a fakh-man?

00:11:07.583 --> 00:11:11.563
a fakh-man, ya, ⟨ot⟩ trakht oys vos nit iz.

